      "writtenOn": "2026-06-05T08:39:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "@elouan.lesteven@cea.fr how does ldiskfs work wrt to packaging ? Do you need lustre/lustre-client/lustre-devel to use it ? Is it part of those packages ? Is it another package ?\n\nIf it\u0027s the same packages, or if lustre/lustre-client/lustre-devel are dependencies of the ldiskfs one, then from a practical pov, moving code isn\u0027t necessary and this one works perfectly. If not, then yeah, moving the code might be later.",
      "parentUuid": "9c8ad6ef_22a29816",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 244,
        "startChar": 27,
        "endLine": 244,
        "endChar": 33
      },
